2014;;Listen Up Philip;;American;;Alex Ross Perry;;Jason SchwartzmanElisabeth MossJonathan Pryce;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Listen_Up_Philip;;Philip (Jason Schwartzman) is an acclaimed but abrasive young writer waiting for the publication of his second novel. He feels bored of his daily life and his shaky relationship with photographer girlfriend Ashley (Elisabeth Moss). In all of this chaos, his idol, veteran novelist Ike Zimmerman (Jonathan Pryce), offers him accommodation at his summer home, an isolated place where he might find peace.